f=Brand Studio/kai/custom/marketing-dashboards/SKILL.md · in=marketing-dashboards kai's recurring scorecard: sections period NSM guardrails (vista's definitions), spend CAC channel, funnel stages, organic social (pulse's numbers), email, SEO movement computed against brand-context baselines vista's targets, reds flagged configured contact. department's self-grading gets reconciled: platform-reported ROAS (rio), platform analytics (pulse) meet kai's independent read, deltas reported, smoothed. · p=scorecard changes shape week teaches nobody anything; metrics without baselines decoration; channel numbers graded channels themselves inflate quietly. fixed-shape, baseline-anchored, reconciled scorecard fixes three reds department's early-warning system, feeding nate's aim, rio's guardrails, vista's roadmap reality. · wu=Triggers: "weekly marketing report," "scorecard," "how week go," configured reporting cadence. · st:/ Protocol=`Pull the period's data (configured sources per channel; operator exports where no connector) \· -> Load brand-context baselines + vista's targets (NSM/guardrails/KRs where set) \· -> Compute the fixed sections; every number = value \· vs baseline \· vs target \· -> RECONCILE: platform-reported vs kai-independent where both exist; deltas reported \· -> Flag reds (breach rules from config) → escalation contact + the owning agent` · h3:Phase Pull Load=Sources config (`metrics_sources` channel; unconnected operator export, as-of dated). Baselines brand-context; targets vista's NSM spec current KRs they exist they don't, scorecard says "no target set" rather inventing one. · h3:Phase Compute Fixed Shape=`assets/scorecard-template.md`: sections, order, period. New sections added deliberately (config change), improvised trend integrity beats novelty. Numbers unavailable period shown gaps, never carried forward silently. · h3:Phase 3 — Reconcile=platform grades itself (ad ROAS, social reach), kai's independent read (site analytics, revenue data) sits beside delta scorecard line. Persistent large deltas their finding (attribution problem rio's playbook refresh, instrumentation problem queue). · h3:Phase Flag Publish=Reds configured breach rules (e.g., guardrail threshold crossed, KPI under baseline periods operator-set, never defaulted). red routes escalation contact *and* owning agent (funnel red nate; ROAS red rio; engagement red pulse). scorecard appends history; deltas-on-deltas (trends) ride along. · of=template: header (period, sources, gaps), fixed sections, reconciliation lines, reds routing, one "what changed" paragraph plain language. · pr=**Same shape period.** Trend integrity product., **Every number: value, baseline, target (or "no target set").**, **Self-graded numbers sit beside independent reads; deltas reported, smoothed.**, **Reds route owners, upward.**, **Gaps shown, never silently carried forward.**, **Breach rules operator-set** (rule 0.5 kai never invents what counts red). · f=connectors operator exports cadence; scorecard states as-of basis., baselines scorecard runs value-only, labeled, while brand-context builds., vista targets baseline-relative only, "no target set" shown standing nudge, blocker. · b:with Other Skills=`brand-context` (sibling) supplies baselines; `seo-strategist` (sibling) supplies SEO section's interpretation., **vista** owns NSM/guardrail definitions targets (kai measures them); **pulse/rio/nate/lena** their channels (kai grades them independently); **echo** consumes scorecard investor updates; **marcus/board** see reds cross strategic fiduciary lines., **The instrumentation queue** (kai's) collects gap scorecard exposes.